{"id": "1191027351560142918", "channel_id": "1191027351560142918", "type": 0, "author_id": "1187994440019746886", "author_name": "kkklavier", "author_bot": false, "content": "想請問前面的劇情在遊戲裡有哪裡能找到連貫的統整版嗎😂\n還是要看一定要再打過一次關卡XDD\n這樣有點太麻煩，而且斷斷續續很難複習\n如果沒有的話希望可以新增這個功能\n感謝🙏🏻", "timestamp": "2023-12-31T14:37:28.830000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1191027351560142918", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」每一章連貫劇情統整", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1181168158678204497"]}
